Bottleneck            Solution
Database Contention "If 10 consumers try to update the same row, they will block each other. 
                    Use Optimistic Locking or separate your data into independent shards."
CPU Saturation       "Do not create 100 threads if you only have 8 CPU cores. 
                    The ""Context Switching"" overhead will actually make the app slower."
