5. Deployment & CI/CD
    Since you are using Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS), future extensions involve:
    Blue-Green or Canary Deployments: Use Kubernetes services to route a small percentage of traffic to a "New Product Service" to test features before a full rollout.
    Helm Charts: Standardize your sbk8-poc deployment configurations so you can easily spin up "Dev," "QA," and "Prod" environments with different resource limits.
